1
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:34,048
=The Glamorous Night=

2
00:01:34,754 --> 00:01:40,712
(Wang Hao)

3
00:01:41,058 --> 00:01:42,259
Ms. Zhao, it's bad.

4
00:01:42,459 --> 00:01:45,298
Mr. Xu's case last night was deemed
sexual harassment by the company.

5
00:01:45,298 --> 00:01:46,536
They declared zero tolerance.

6
00:01:47,099 --> 00:01:48,138
What should we do now?

7
00:01:48,619 --> 00:01:49,619
(Sexual harassment?)

8
00:01:50,418 --> 00:01:51,459
(Zero tolerance?)

9
00:01:53,659 --> 00:01:54,498
(My career)

10
00:01:54,498 --> 00:01:57,179
(won't be ruined
over such an absurd thing, will it?)

11
00:02:02,082 --> 00:02:05,653
(16 hours earlier)

12
00:02:13,698 --> 00:02:16,219
(Zhao Mei, Head of Promotions
& Deputy Sales Director, GST Liquor China)

13
00:02:16,219 --> 00:02:17,224
(My name is Zhao Mei.)

14
00:02:17,418 --> 00:02:18,499
(I'm 32 years old.)

15
00:02:19,418 --> 00:02:20,418
(I started at 20.)

16
00:02:20,698 --> 00:02:23,138
(I've been hustling
and smiling through it all)

17
00:02:23,339 --> 00:02:24,219
(and finally become)

18
00:02:24,219 --> 00:02:26,578
(the Deputy Director of Promotions
at GST Liquor.)

19
00:02:27,698 --> 00:02:30,819
(It sounds fancy, but I'm just the head
of the sales ladies.)

20
00:02:32,099 --> 00:02:34,099
(There are two kinds of people
in the world.)

21
00:02:34,259 --> 00:02:36,379
(One kind cherishes the present
and is content.)

22
00:02:36,578 --> 00:02:38,418
(The other kind is like me,)

23
00:02:38,738 --> 00:02:40,659
(always aiming for higher places)

24
00:02:40,939 --> 00:02:42,379
- (and better titles.)
- It's me?

25
00:02:43,698 --> 00:02:45,379
(The opportunity has finally come.)

26
00:02:45,939 --> 00:02:47,618
- (My immediate superior, Xu Yuntian,)
- Thank you, sir.

27
00:02:47,618 --> 00:02:49,819
(is about to be promoted to Sales VP.)

28
00:02:50,458 --> 00:02:52,939
(Tonight is the celebration party
prepared for him.)

29
00:02:53,339 --> 00:02:54,099
(I've decided.)

30
00:02:55,099 --> 00:02:56,379
(I'll give it my best shot.)

31
00:03:29,099 --> 00:03:30,298
And this.

32
00:03:30,298 --> 00:03:32,659
Thirty-year-old single malt whisky.

33
00:03:37,099 --> 00:03:37,779
I'm here.

34
00:03:39,298 --> 00:03:40,219
Why are you so late?

35
00:03:40,779 --> 00:03:42,059
See if you want anything else.

36
00:03:42,259 --> 00:03:44,178
(Liang Danning)
Don't mention it. I'm really unlucky.

37
00:03:44,539 --> 00:03:45,178
(Sales Manager, GST Liquor China)
What's wrong?

38
00:03:45,819 --> 00:03:46,698
My husband

39
00:03:47,048 --> 00:03:49,219
stole the wine I bought
during the staff internal sale

40
00:03:49,219 --> 00:03:51,738
and got caught red-handed
by internal audit when reselling it.

41
00:03:52,539 --> 00:03:53,458
Internal audit?

42
00:03:58,178 --> 00:03:59,379
So annoying.

43
00:04:00,499 --> 00:04:03,298
(She's Liang Danning,
my best friend for ten years.)

44
00:04:03,659 --> 00:04:04,939
(As a top salesperson,)

45
00:04:05,219 --> 00:04:06,979
(she's known as the flower of GST.)

46
00:04:07,819 --> 00:04:09,138
(A very nice person.)

47
00:04:09,418 --> 00:04:10,379
- (Too bad her husband...)
- Boss.

48
00:04:10,578 --> 00:04:11,578
(is very bad.)

49
00:04:12,259 --> 00:04:15,259
There's something
I might need to trouble you with.

50
00:04:15,259 --> 00:04:17,539
I was hoping you could
put in a word with internal audit

51
00:04:17,539 --> 00:04:18,979
and help me plead with them.

52
00:04:19,139 --> 00:04:20,738
I'm not on great terms with them.

53
00:04:20,938 --> 00:04:21,659
I can only try.

54
00:04:21,659 --> 00:04:23,019
Boss, have you arrived at Cocoon?

55
00:04:23,178 --> 00:04:23,938
I've arrived.

56
00:04:23,938 --> 00:04:26,258
(He is Dong Yue,
Deputy Director of Sales.)

57
00:04:26,539 --> 00:04:27,699
(Liang Danning's superior)

58
00:04:27,858 --> 00:04:29,339
- (and my peer.)
- Come back.

59
00:04:29,339 --> 00:04:31,258
(Dong Yue)
(The difference is, he's in sales.)

60
00:04:31,459 --> 00:04:32,258
(Deputy Sales Director, GST Liquor China)
(I'm in promotion.)

61
00:04:33,019 --> 00:04:33,818
(I bet)

62
00:04:34,378 --> 00:04:35,219
(he's just like me,)

63
00:04:35,378 --> 00:04:38,258
(eyeing the vacancy
after Xu Yuntian's promotion.)

64
00:04:38,738 --> 00:04:40,099
(Otherwise, why would he ditch)

65
00:04:40,378 --> 00:04:41,979
(his sugar mommy
on a weekend like this?)

66
00:04:42,378 --> 00:04:42,878
Well?

67
00:04:43,339 --> 00:04:43,839
You can go.

68
00:04:44,139 --> 00:04:44,979
(But it's right.)

69
00:04:45,618 --> 00:04:48,139
(Nothing beats having your own.)

70
00:04:51,139 --> 00:04:53,339
I heard Xu will be promoted to VP.

71
00:04:54,539 --> 00:04:56,058
You're quite well-informed.

72
00:04:56,258 --> 00:04:59,336
No wonder they made all of us
in Guangzhou come over.

73
00:04:59,688 --> 00:05:03,178
So it wasn't to support Cocoon,
but to support himself all along.

74
00:05:04,899 --> 00:05:06,339
Xu should be coming soon.

75
00:05:06,979 --> 00:05:07,858
I'll head over first.

76
00:05:08,219 --> 00:05:08,938
Hurry.

77
00:05:09,339 --> 00:05:11,298
Make sure you flatter him well tonight.

78
00:05:11,858 --> 00:05:13,378
Ladies and gentlemen,

79
00:05:14,058 --> 00:05:15,498
are you ready?

80
00:05:16,459 --> 00:05:17,498
Thank you all for coming

81
00:05:17,498 --> 00:05:19,219
to the grand opening of Cocoon Club.

82
00:05:19,539 --> 00:05:22,019
Tonight's attendees are all Cocoon's
most distinguished guests

83
00:05:22,019 --> 00:05:23,818
and, even more, its most valued friends.

84
00:05:24,298 --> 00:05:26,298
Raise your hands and follow my rhythm.

85
00:05:26,298 --> 00:05:28,899
Let's enjoy the party together.

86
00:05:41,258 --> 00:05:42,339
Boss, you're here.

87
00:05:42,498 --> 00:05:43,418
You arrived early.

88
00:05:43,699 --> 00:05:44,938
I had to welcome you.

89
00:05:46,019 --> 00:05:47,019
Hello, boss.

90
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:47,699
You're here.

91
00:05:47,699 --> 00:05:48,298
Hello, boss.

92
00:05:48,298 --> 00:05:48,858
Boss.

93
00:05:52,459 --> 00:05:53,858
(The star of tonight has arrived.)

94
00:05:54,418 --> 00:05:55,779
(This is my boss)

95
00:05:56,058 --> 00:05:58,139
(Xu Yuntian)
(and my rock for a decade:)

96
00:05:58,219 --> 00:06:01,339
(Sales Director, GST Liquor China)
(Xu Yuntian, Sales Director of GST China.)

97
00:06:02,216 --> 00:06:03,858
(Some wish for their husbands' success.)

98
00:06:03,858 --> 00:06:05,858
(Yet I constantly hope
for my boss's success.)

99
00:06:06,459 --> 00:06:08,579
(After all,
that's the rule of the workplace.)

100
00:06:09,178 --> 00:06:11,699
(One rises, all rise.)

101
00:06:16,178 --> 00:06:17,339
Mei, watch your step.

102
00:06:20,418 --> 00:06:21,699
This way, please.

103
00:06:25,339 --> 00:06:28,099
Boss, this table
is reserved for the big shots.

104
00:06:28,099 --> 00:06:29,539
They want to come here tonight.

105
00:06:30,298 --> 00:06:31,378
We'll see.

106
00:06:32,818 --> 00:06:33,579
Can we sit here?

107
00:06:33,779 --> 00:06:34,418
Sure.

108
00:06:34,539 --> 00:06:37,579
Mr. Xu, you can sit wherever you want.
This is your turf.

109
00:06:38,298 --> 00:06:38,798
Come.

110
00:06:38,998 --> 00:06:39,498
Well?

111
00:06:39,498 --> 00:06:40,488
Mr. Xu, what's the plan?

112
00:06:41,378 --> 00:06:42,858
Just serve whatever. I'm easy.

113
00:06:44,139 --> 00:06:45,779
You're always so generous.

114
00:06:46,019 --> 00:06:47,339
We're all family here.

115
00:06:47,498 --> 00:06:48,178
Bring the drinks.

116
00:06:48,178 --> 00:06:49,178
Got it. Right away.

117
00:06:54,298 --> 00:06:55,099
Come on.

118
00:06:55,258 --> 00:06:55,779
Come on.

119
00:06:55,779 --> 00:06:57,219
To Mr. Xu's continuous success!

120
00:06:57,318 --> 00:06:57,818
Cheers!

121
00:06:57,818 --> 00:06:59,298
We're just riding your coattails.

122
00:07:05,938 --> 00:07:06,779
Andy.

123
00:07:07,339 --> 00:07:08,339
Your boss is something.

124
00:07:08,779 --> 00:07:10,019
Business is so tough right now.

125
00:07:10,139 --> 00:07:12,459
Yet he's still spending money
on this opening?

126
00:07:13,298 --> 00:07:15,938
It's all thanks to Mr. Xu
and everyone's support.

127
00:07:16,779 --> 00:07:17,659
Where's Shen?

128
00:07:18,019 --> 00:07:19,258
Probably stuck in traffic now.

129
00:07:19,258 --> 00:07:20,139
I'll go check it out.

130
00:07:20,858 --> 00:07:22,618
Right. Thank you.

131
00:07:22,659 --> 00:07:23,418
Go check it out.

132
00:07:23,418 --> 00:07:23,918
Okay.

133
00:07:26,099 --> 00:07:27,339
(Another suck-up's arrived.)

134
00:07:28,099 --> 00:07:30,899
(Tang Lide, another Deputy Sales Director
at our company.)

135
00:07:31,058 --> 00:07:32,899
(Tang Lide, Sales Deputy Director)
(The slickest old fox in the office.)

136
00:07:33,298 --> 00:07:35,699
(He flew back just to kiss up
and show loyalty.)

137
00:07:36,178 --> 00:07:37,699
(To entertain the boss tonight,)

138
00:07:38,019 --> 00:07:40,899
(he flew back
from a business trip in Shanghai.)

139
00:07:41,459 --> 00:07:43,818
(Rumor has it he's flying back
first thing tomorrow.)

140
00:07:45,219 --> 00:07:46,378
(What a tough guy.)

141
00:07:47,298 --> 00:07:49,019
Boss, when I heard

142
00:07:49,139 --> 00:07:51,219
that you became the Sales VP,

143
00:07:51,219 --> 00:07:52,779
I got so pumped up.

144
00:07:53,699 --> 00:07:54,339
Come on.

145
00:07:54,339 --> 00:07:55,099
Come on.

146
00:07:55,298 --> 00:07:56,738
Let me congratulate you,

147
00:07:56,738 --> 00:07:58,858
wishing you boundless success!

148
00:07:58,858 --> 00:07:59,899
I appreciate it.

149
00:08:04,328 --> 00:08:05,418
Late-night snacks later?

150
00:08:05,438 --> 00:08:05,938
Boss.

151
00:08:05,938 --> 00:08:06,498
My treat.

152
00:08:07,139 --> 00:08:08,579
I need to tell you something.

153
00:08:09,298 --> 00:08:10,219
I was looking for you.

154
00:08:11,938 --> 00:08:13,298
For such a big party tonight,

155
00:08:14,618 --> 00:08:16,899
you only assigned two female sales reps?

156
00:08:17,058 --> 00:08:18,618
Do you think that's appropriate?

157
00:08:19,139 --> 00:08:23,178
Tang, it's always easy for you to say.

158
00:08:23,339 --> 00:08:24,618
Those two sales ladies

159
00:08:24,618 --> 00:08:26,899
were transferred from other branches.

160
00:08:26,938 --> 00:08:30,058
Nowadays, all pretty girls
become influencers or streamer.

161
00:08:30,058 --> 00:08:32,179
Don't you watch those streams every day?

162
00:08:32,579 --> 00:08:35,419
Besides, our boss isn't lacking
for beauties.

163
00:08:35,459 --> 00:08:36,378
Right, boss?

164
00:08:36,378 --> 00:08:37,299
Not lacking beauties?

165
00:08:37,459 --> 00:08:38,979
Where are the beauties?

166
00:08:38,979 --> 00:08:39,538
See?

167
00:08:42,018 --> 00:08:44,099
His eyes light up
at the word 'beauties.'

168
00:08:45,979 --> 00:08:46,819
Come on.

169
00:08:53,378 --> 00:08:54,858
Whispering in the boss's ear again.

170
00:08:56,299 --> 00:08:58,059
Don't make baseless accusations.

171
00:09:00,618 --> 00:09:03,939
Clearly, you've never been targeted.

172
00:09:04,339 --> 00:09:05,618
Everything looks rosy to you.

173
00:09:07,819 --> 00:09:08,618
Stop.

174
00:09:08,778 --> 00:09:09,939
Stop.

175
00:09:09,939 --> 00:09:11,179
You can't park here.

176
00:09:11,179 --> 00:09:11,699
Move.

177
00:09:11,699 --> 00:09:12,819
Move now. Hear me?

178
00:09:13,138 --> 00:09:13,638
Move it.

179
00:09:14,658 --> 00:09:16,538
Are you blind? That's our boss's car.

180
00:09:17,179 --> 00:09:18,099
Don't come tomorrow.

181
00:09:18,099 --> 00:09:19,658
Forget it. It's nothing.

182
00:09:20,658 --> 00:09:21,538
Sorry, boss. He's new.

183
00:09:21,538 --> 00:09:22,778
Let's back up a bit.

184
00:09:24,138 --> 00:09:25,699
You put guys like this on the front?

185
00:09:26,299 --> 00:09:27,099
Sorry, boss.

186
00:09:31,059 --> 00:09:32,018
My bad, handsome.

187
00:09:32,018 --> 00:09:32,538
Sorry.

188
00:09:33,858 --> 00:09:36,219
(Shen Mo, Cocoon owner)
(This is Cocoon's owner,)

189
00:09:36,579 --> 00:09:39,579
(GST Liquor Tier-1 Distributor)
(Shen Mo, GST's Tier-1 Distributor.)

190
00:09:40,138 --> 00:09:42,059
(On the surface,
he sells wine for our company)

191
00:09:42,059 --> 00:09:43,699
(and serves our company.)

192
00:09:44,299 --> 00:09:47,179
(But he's fronted
so much capital for us)

193
00:09:47,378 --> 00:09:49,778
(that he's become our biggest client.)

194
00:09:51,018 --> 00:09:53,858
(I think he actually
looks down on Xu Yuntian.)

195
00:09:54,419 --> 00:09:56,378
(No matter how arrogant Xu is,)

196
00:09:56,939 --> 00:09:58,219
(he's still just an employee.)

197
00:09:58,699 --> 00:10:01,258
This street turns pitch black at night.

198
00:10:01,498 --> 00:10:03,339
Frankly, I can't stand it.

199
00:10:03,939 --> 00:10:05,538
Cocoon might be small,

200
00:10:05,898 --> 00:10:07,179
but I really want to see

201
00:10:07,658 --> 00:10:09,939
if it can light up this street.

202
00:10:29,498 --> 00:10:30,059
Andy, come.

203
00:10:30,059 --> 00:10:30,618
Mr. Xu.

204
00:10:33,459 --> 00:10:35,138
Where's your boss?
Still stuck in traffic?

205
00:10:36,138 --> 00:10:36,738
Sorry.

206
00:10:36,738 --> 00:10:37,459
I was too busy

207
00:10:37,459 --> 00:10:38,498
and forgot to tell you.

208
00:10:38,699 --> 00:10:39,378
My boss is here.

209
00:10:39,738 --> 00:10:42,099
Some suppliers and peers are with him.

210
00:10:42,099 --> 00:10:44,138
He'll come to keep you company
once they leave.

211
00:10:45,018 --> 00:10:46,018
Is he avoiding me?

212
00:10:46,138 --> 00:10:47,658
No, not at all.

213
00:10:48,059 --> 00:10:49,898
Alright, I'll check it out for you.

214
00:10:53,778 --> 00:10:54,579
No weaseling out.

215
00:10:54,579 --> 00:10:55,258
Bottoms up!

216
00:10:55,579 --> 00:10:56,520
Everyone, bottoms up!

217
00:11:00,579 --> 00:11:01,538
You go with Andy.

218
00:11:02,179 --> 00:11:03,378
See if Mr. Shen is there.

219
00:11:03,378 --> 00:11:04,138
If he is,

220
00:11:04,618 --> 00:11:06,579
tell him to front
another 3,000 cases of Gennadiy.

221
00:11:18,618 --> 00:11:21,898
(Is Xu getting a bit too cocky?)

222
00:11:23,099 --> 00:11:24,618
(Hard to tell if it's good or bad.)

223
00:11:33,258 --> 00:11:33,819
Who are you?

224
00:11:34,219 --> 00:11:35,419
I'm Tommy from Sales.

225
00:11:35,538 --> 00:11:37,099
(Tommy, Sales, GST Liquor China)
How come I've never seen you before?

226
00:11:37,419 --> 00:11:38,179
Sorry.

227
00:11:38,179 --> 00:11:39,258
(Zeng Zixuan, Sales Lady, GST Liquor)
I've been at the day store before.

228
00:11:39,258 --> 00:11:41,059
It's my first time helping
at the nightclub.

229
00:11:47,738 --> 00:11:48,979
Mr. Xu is here tonight.

230
00:11:49,018 --> 00:11:50,018
Have you toasted him?

231
00:11:50,179 --> 00:11:50,738
No.

232
00:11:51,658 --> 00:11:53,099
What are you waiting for?

233
00:11:53,099 --> 00:11:53,939
Hurry up and go.

234
00:11:53,939 --> 00:11:55,979
No, we sales ladies have rules.

235
00:11:55,979 --> 00:11:57,658
We can't drink during work hours.

236
00:11:57,658 --> 00:11:59,258
And we can't leave our posts.

237
00:12:00,538 --> 00:12:01,059
Look.

238
00:12:02,219 --> 00:12:02,898
Look.

239
00:12:04,579 --> 00:12:05,898
Isn't Zhao Mei your supervisor?

240
00:12:06,618 --> 00:12:08,898
When she was young,
she was also a sales lady.

241
00:12:09,419 --> 00:12:12,179
If she were as stubborn as you,
how could she be where she is today?

242
00:12:12,738 --> 00:12:14,339
What do you think she relied on?

243
00:12:14,738 --> 00:12:16,459
Relying on following store rules?

244
00:12:16,939 --> 00:12:20,258
Or being invisible in front of the boss
and standing still?

245
00:12:20,819 --> 00:12:21,738
Miss,

246
00:12:22,099 --> 00:12:24,898
Mr. Xu has finally come tonight.

247
00:12:26,059 --> 00:12:28,699
You need to seize this opportunity,
you know?

248
00:12:31,498 --> 00:12:32,618
I... I can't.

249
00:12:35,219 --> 00:12:39,618
You need to bravely charge
towards the boss.

250
00:12:49,299 --> 00:12:50,299
Mission accomplished?

251
00:12:50,979 --> 00:12:51,658
It's hard.

252
00:12:51,738 --> 00:12:52,419
Why alone?

253
00:12:52,498 --> 00:12:53,339
What?

254
00:12:53,538 --> 00:12:54,858
I said, why are you alone?

255
00:12:55,579 --> 00:12:56,658
I came out to take a break.

256
00:12:59,658 --> 00:13:00,419
I heard

257
00:13:00,538 --> 00:13:01,858
one of your sales ladies

258
00:13:01,858 --> 00:13:03,258
eloped with a fruit seller.

259
00:13:04,339 --> 00:13:05,378
You know that?

260
00:13:05,858 --> 00:13:07,738
It was in our sales chat.
How could I not know?

261
00:13:08,138 --> 00:13:09,138
It's not elopement.

262
00:13:09,498 --> 00:13:10,344
She's unmarried.

263
00:13:10,344 --> 00:13:12,778
Her family set up an engagement
for her without her consent.

264
00:13:12,778 --> 00:13:14,138
She doesn't even know that guy.

265
00:13:15,138 --> 00:13:15,658
No.

266
00:13:15,658 --> 00:13:18,498
Mr. Xu, I'm Zeng Zixuan
from the Promotions Department.

267
00:13:18,618 --> 00:13:19,118
What?

268
00:13:19,219 --> 00:13:21,579
I'm Zeng Zixuan.
I'd like to offer you a toast.

269
00:13:37,736 --> 00:13:40,378
You don't know how hard it is
to manage young people these days.

270
00:13:40,618 --> 00:13:42,538
Especially places full of pretty girls.

271
00:13:43,579 --> 00:13:46,299
Mr. Xu, let me pour you another drink.

272
00:13:50,179 --> 00:13:50,792
Are you okay?

273
00:13:51,018 --> 00:13:51,579
Mr. Xu.

274
00:13:52,579 --> 00:13:54,099
Everyone has their own thoughts.

275
00:13:54,419 --> 00:13:55,658
Strict management won't work.

276
00:13:56,579 --> 00:13:58,658
By the way, you're good at this.

277
00:14:03,219 --> 00:14:05,898
Xu has had enough to drink.
He's at it again.

278
00:14:06,299 --> 00:14:07,579
Speak of the devil.

279
00:14:08,099 --> 00:14:09,138
And someone's filming.

280
00:14:10,378 --> 00:14:11,258
Who is this girl?

281
00:14:12,618 --> 00:14:13,459
Don't ruin the mood.

282
00:14:14,258 --> 00:14:15,258
That's my person.

283
00:14:16,419 --> 00:14:17,219
Boss.

284
00:14:17,858 --> 00:14:18,979
Boss, let go.

285
00:14:19,138 --> 00:14:20,738
None of your business. Stay away.

286
00:14:20,939 --> 00:14:21,979
Boss, sober up.

287
00:14:22,339 --> 00:14:25,099
Mind your own business.
She came on her own.

288
00:14:25,378 --> 00:14:27,099
We're here today to support Mr. Shen.

289
00:14:27,099 --> 00:14:27,939
People are watching.

290
00:14:27,939 --> 00:14:28,979
Don't embarrass yourself.

291
00:14:29,219 --> 00:14:31,099
I don't care who is watching.

292
00:14:31,258 --> 00:14:32,699
Stop messing around, okay?

293
00:14:33,498 --> 00:14:34,898
You're overstepping.

294
00:14:35,258 --> 00:14:36,498
If she can't, you do it.

295
00:14:37,339 --> 00:14:38,179
Wake up.

296
00:14:38,498 --> 00:14:39,258
Stay calm.

297
00:14:39,258 --> 00:14:40,138
Stay calm, okay?

298
00:14:40,138 --> 00:14:41,339
This is too explosive.

299
00:14:41,778 --> 00:14:42,939
I'll post it in the group.

300
00:14:47,018 --> 00:14:48,018
Slow down. Take care.

301
00:14:53,138 --> 00:14:54,018
I have to say,

302
00:14:54,939 --> 00:14:57,419
the young ladies nowadays
are so ambitious.

303
00:14:57,579 --> 00:15:00,658
Seeing the boss,
they'll eagerly rush to toast him.

304
00:15:04,179 --> 00:15:05,858
I remember our company has rules, right?

305
00:15:05,858 --> 00:15:06,898
Sales ladies

306
00:15:07,219 --> 00:15:08,498
can't drink while working.

307
00:15:08,959 --> 00:15:09,459
You...

308
00:15:09,459 --> 00:15:10,819
- Let me tell you.
- Your talking woke me.

309
00:15:10,819 --> 00:15:12,738
I talk nonsense when I'm drunk.

310
00:15:13,939 --> 00:15:14,498
Ignore him.

311
00:15:15,018 --> 00:15:16,299
You were so tough back there.

312
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:18,939
I splashed him before I realized it.
I did it for his own good.

313
00:15:18,939 --> 00:15:19,439
It's fine.

314
00:15:32,138 --> 00:15:32,778
Come with me.

315
00:15:38,018 --> 00:15:38,939
Sorry, boss.

316
00:15:39,099 --> 00:15:41,459
It was Tommy from Sales
who urged me to toast.

317
00:15:42,738 --> 00:15:44,658
(Using my person
to curry favor with Xu.)

318
00:15:45,699 --> 00:15:47,459
(Then it seems I mismanaged things.)

319
00:15:48,258 --> 00:15:50,579
(These guys really see me
as a pushover.)

320
00:15:51,738 --> 00:15:53,618
(Alright. I'll fire her.)

321
00:15:54,219 --> 00:15:56,099
(Tomorrow, when Xu sobers up,
I'll go act cute.)

322
00:15:56,939 --> 00:15:58,939
(Let's see where you can stab me next.)

323
00:16:07,339 --> 00:16:08,778
Right.

324
00:16:08,898 --> 00:16:10,538
I have a ton of things to do right now.

325
00:16:10,538 --> 00:16:11,219
Super busy.

326
00:16:11,618 --> 00:16:12,712
Linda, the boss wants you.

327
00:16:22,339 --> 00:16:22,839
Qinru,

328
00:16:23,378 --> 00:16:24,219
look.

329
00:16:27,234 --> 00:16:27,752
(Wang Hao)

330
00:16:32,098 --> 00:16:33,256
(EXPOSED: Corporate Executive
Gropes a Woman at Nightclub)

331
00:16:34,626 --> 00:16:35,336
(Sexual Harassment)

332
00:16:37,314 --> 00:16:42,370
=Episode 1=
(Employee Zhao Mei)

333
00:16:42,626 --> 00:16:44,692
(Li Dongming,
Senior Partner, Ruijin Consulting)

334
00:16:45,138 --> 00:16:45,658
You're awake.

335
00:16:46,819 --> 00:16:47,699
Did you see the news?

336
00:16:48,538 --> 00:16:51,099
I think Xu Yuntian
is in deep trouble this time.

337
00:17:01,059 --> 00:17:02,179
I really didn't expect this.

338
00:17:03,778 --> 00:17:05,416
You don't think he's innocent, do you?

339
00:17:06,738 --> 00:17:07,659
No, not that.

340
00:17:08,264 --> 00:17:09,379
I just feel a bit uneasy.

341
00:17:10,939 --> 00:17:12,778
A public storm of this scale

342
00:17:13,538 --> 00:17:14,659
couldn't be accidental.

343
00:17:19,859 --> 00:17:21,778
There's a white hair here.
Pull it out for me.

344
00:17:22,899 --> 00:17:25,778
Your company is preparing
for organizational restructuring.

345
00:17:26,379 --> 00:17:28,139
Fan assigned this task to me.

346
00:17:29,699 --> 00:17:31,419
'Organizational restructuring'?

347
00:17:32,538 --> 00:17:33,738
Isn't that just layoffs?

348
00:17:33,859 --> 00:17:36,139
It is layoffs.
Just like plucking white hairs.

349
00:17:36,899 --> 00:17:39,498
With poor sales and profits,
layoffs are normal for a company.

350
00:17:40,179 --> 00:17:42,219
Our company is preparing layoffs too.

351
00:17:49,298 --> 00:17:52,379
No wonder the head of internal audit
suddenly approached me last night.

352
00:17:53,098 --> 00:17:54,258
Approached you? What for?

353
00:17:55,859 --> 00:17:57,459
(Sun Yu)
Regarding sales compliance,

354
00:17:58,058 --> 00:17:59,459
(Head of Internal Audit, GST Liquor China)
the company is taking it very seriously.

355
00:18:01,219 --> 00:18:02,619
I can't tell you

356
00:18:03,058 --> 00:18:04,498
the details right now.

357
00:18:04,818 --> 00:18:07,058
But we've hired a third-party team
to investigate.

358
00:18:07,979 --> 00:18:09,659
You're a long-time employee at GST,

359
00:18:10,018 --> 00:18:13,258
managing the Promotions Department,
which is closely tied to sales.

360
00:18:14,778 --> 00:18:16,778
If you have any valuable information,

361
00:18:17,219 --> 00:18:18,778
no matter how high up it goes,

362
00:18:19,338 --> 00:18:20,459
feel free to contact me.

363
00:18:21,098 --> 00:18:23,400
He basically wanted me
to provide evidence against Xu.

364
00:18:24,098 --> 00:18:24,979
Did you provide any?

365
00:18:25,818 --> 00:18:26,939
Of course not.

366
00:18:28,219 --> 00:18:30,018
But isn't this way too fast?

367
00:18:30,818 --> 00:18:32,939
He approached me yesterday,
and today Xu's fired?

368
00:18:33,899 --> 00:18:35,619
If they came prepared,

369
00:18:35,859 --> 00:18:37,538
layoffs can happen in an instant.

370
00:18:39,058 --> 00:18:41,298
So you're saying
this so-called sexual harassment

371
00:18:41,498 --> 00:18:43,058
is a setup to take down Xu?

372
00:18:44,018 --> 00:18:45,258
It's highly possible.

373
00:18:46,298 --> 00:18:47,738
Xu Yuntian has been at your company

374
00:18:48,018 --> 00:18:49,498
for over twenty years, right?

375
00:18:49,899 --> 00:18:51,338
Using a sexual harassment incident

376
00:18:51,578 --> 00:18:54,778
to get rid of an executive
with twenty-plus years of service

377
00:18:54,979 --> 00:18:56,219
might be crude and simple,

378
00:18:57,258 --> 00:19:00,298
but it wins on being efficient
and cost-effective.

379
00:19:02,979 --> 00:19:04,498
That's so cold-blooded.

380
00:19:05,619 --> 00:19:08,018
Stop just thinking about him.
Think about yourself.

381
00:19:09,098 --> 00:19:11,219
Your company will use this
to purge certain people.

382
00:19:11,738 --> 00:19:13,298
Given your ties with Xu Yuntian,

383
00:19:13,459 --> 00:19:15,219
you're very likely the next one
to be axed.

384
00:19:17,314 --> 00:19:18,368
(Darn it.)

385
00:19:23,578 --> 00:19:24,778
Smoking kills.

386
00:19:25,538 --> 00:19:26,578
So you're giving up?

387
00:19:26,939 --> 00:19:29,058
How can I have fighting spirit
after what you said?

388
00:19:30,498 --> 00:19:31,738
I think you're right.

389
00:19:31,939 --> 00:19:34,018
Xu personally promoted me.

390
00:19:34,379 --> 00:19:36,179
If he gets taken down,
how could I be safe?

391
00:19:36,459 --> 00:19:37,179
No.

392
00:19:37,738 --> 00:19:39,459
You can't get fired right now.

393
00:19:39,899 --> 00:19:40,699
Think about it.

394
00:19:41,459 --> 00:19:43,219
Xu Yuntian gets fired
for sexual harassment.

395
00:19:43,498 --> 00:19:44,899
If you immediately get fired too,

396
00:19:45,018 --> 00:19:46,818
given the girl harassed
was your subordinate,

397
00:19:47,139 --> 00:19:48,419
how will others see this?

398
00:19:48,719 --> 00:19:50,058
Won't they think you offered

399
00:19:50,058 --> 00:19:51,098
that girl to Xu Yuntian?

400
00:19:51,498 --> 00:19:52,979
How many times have you done it?

401
00:19:53,659 --> 00:19:54,738
How many girls were hurt?

402
00:19:54,979 --> 00:19:57,338
You're a woman. What was
your relationship with Xu Yuntian?

403
00:19:57,859 --> 00:20:00,018
You know my relationship
with Xu was completely proper.

404
00:20:00,338 --> 00:20:02,298
I know, but others don't.

405
00:20:02,578 --> 00:20:04,098
If you get fired at this point,

406
00:20:04,219 --> 00:20:06,459
it'll ruin your reputation.

407
00:20:07,139 --> 00:20:09,338
If that happens,
you won't just lose your job at GST.

408
00:20:09,899 --> 00:20:10,939
Industry-wide,

409
00:20:10,939 --> 00:20:12,838
finding work anywhere
after this will be tough.

410
00:20:19,139 --> 00:20:20,939
So, what do you think I should do?

411
00:20:23,738 --> 00:20:24,659
Let's split up.

412
00:20:24,899 --> 00:20:27,459
You go to the office as usual
and see what's happening.

413
00:20:27,619 --> 00:20:28,298
As for me,

414
00:20:28,298 --> 00:20:30,659
I planned to have dinner
with your boss these days.

415
00:20:30,778 --> 00:20:32,379
I'll see if I can push it to tonight

416
00:20:32,738 --> 00:20:33,778
to feel him out.

417
00:20:34,659 --> 00:20:35,159
I'm off.

418
00:20:45,498 --> 00:20:47,699
And don't remind others of Xu Yuntian

419
00:20:47,899 --> 00:20:49,818
having promoted you as his trusted aide.

420
00:20:50,058 --> 00:20:51,538
You must distance yourself from him.

421
00:20:54,778 --> 00:20:57,419
Our company approached you last week?

422
00:20:57,738 --> 00:20:59,298
Why are you only telling me now?

423
00:21:01,498 --> 00:21:02,979
Even though you're my wife,

424
00:21:03,979 --> 00:21:05,778
I have my professional ethics to uphold.

425
00:21:07,459 --> 00:21:07,979
I'm off.

426
00:21:16,738 --> 00:21:17,738
(For sexual harassment)

427
00:21:17,738 --> 00:21:20,139
(in the workplace
and all other contexts,)

428
00:21:20,538 --> 00:21:23,298
(GST has always maintained
a zero-tolerance stance.)

429
00:21:23,899 --> 00:21:26,659
(Accordingly,
we will take the following actions:)

430
00:21:27,219 --> 00:21:30,179
(First, Xu Yuntian
has violated company discipline)

431
00:21:30,379 --> 00:21:32,520
(and failed to meet
the required ethical standards.)

432
00:21:32,619 --> 00:21:35,538
(Effective immediately, all his duties
and positions are suspended.)

433
00:21:36,139 --> 00:21:38,419
(Second, we'll thoroughly
investigate this matter)

434
00:21:38,778 --> 00:21:40,859
(to ensure those affected
receive an explanation.)

435
00:21:41,818 --> 00:21:42,979
(Regarding this incident)

436
00:21:42,979 --> 00:21:44,659
(and the distress
it has caused everyone,)

437
00:21:44,939 --> 00:21:46,338
(we sincerely apologize.)

438
00:21:47,338 --> 00:21:48,778
(Since our founding,)

439
00:21:49,298 --> 00:21:51,459
(respecting women
and respecting our employees)

440
00:21:51,859 --> 00:21:53,859
(have always been the bedrock of GST.)

441
00:21:59,379 --> 00:22:00,659
(Unbelievable.)

442
00:22:01,128 --> 00:22:03,298
(Sure, a Director title
isn't that high and mighty,)

443
00:22:03,979 --> 00:22:05,459
(but Xu, as the Sales Director,)

444
00:22:05,859 --> 00:22:06,979
(Promotions Department)
(was genuinely)

445
00:22:06,979 --> 00:22:09,699
(generating billions
in annual revenue for the company.)

446
00:22:10,538 --> 00:22:11,899
(And he was just fired like that?)

447
00:22:12,939 --> 00:22:14,018
(Trophy)
(Who would believe this?)

448
00:22:16,139 --> 00:22:17,098
(Li Dongming was right.)

449
00:22:17,939 --> 00:22:20,538
(At a time like this,
I need to distance myself from Xu.)

450
00:22:21,058 --> 00:22:22,459
(This isn't the time to be seen.)

451
00:22:23,498 --> 00:22:24,619
(I must not let anyone)

452
00:22:24,979 --> 00:22:26,538
(associate me with him anymore.)

453
00:22:37,298 --> 00:22:37,818
Boss,

454
00:22:38,659 --> 00:22:39,179
(Wang Hao)
they

455
00:22:39,578 --> 00:22:41,058
(Promotions Manager, GST Liquor China)
are already raiding Mr. Xu's office.

456
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:44,168
Yesterday he celebrated his promotion.
Today his place is 'raided.'

457
00:22:44,859 --> 00:22:45,538
What?

458
00:22:48,498 --> 00:22:48,998
(Promotions Department)
Boss,

459
00:22:49,778 --> 00:22:50,659
just stay out of this.

460
00:22:50,979 --> 00:22:51,859
What's wrong?

461
00:22:56,899 --> 00:22:58,058
They've taken his computer.

462
00:22:58,379 --> 00:22:59,538
They'll check the data.

463
00:23:07,459 --> 00:23:07,959
Boss.

464
00:23:22,139 --> 00:23:25,219
The Global Outstanding Employee Award.
Personally presented by the chairman.

465
00:23:25,219 --> 00:23:26,632
Only two were awarded nationwide.

466
00:23:27,379 --> 00:23:28,859
As former colleagues,

467
00:23:29,018 --> 00:23:30,018
can you handle it gently?

468
00:23:44,859 --> 00:23:46,098
(Why did I lose my cool again?)

469
00:23:55,899 --> 00:23:57,338
(Zhao Mei)
How's it going on your end?

470
00:23:57,699 --> 00:23:59,258
Is your meeting with our big boss set?

471
00:24:02,778 --> 00:24:03,738
(I was in a meeting.)

472
00:24:04,058 --> 00:24:05,818
(Li Dongming)
(I'm having dinner with your boss)

473
00:24:05,818 --> 00:24:07,538
(and some of the management team
tonight.)

474
00:24:08,058 --> 00:24:10,179
(Stay calm.
Don't do anything unnecessary.)

475
00:24:10,379 --> 00:24:10,979
Go on.

476
00:24:13,459 --> 00:24:15,738
Here's my initial research
on the imported liquor market.

477
00:24:15,746 --> 00:24:16,968
(Chinese Imported Liquor Market
Preliminary Research)

478
00:24:18,379 --> 00:24:19,738
(Qiao Hailun)
Regarding the GST project,

479
00:24:19,939 --> 00:24:21,379
(Junior Analyst, Ruijin Consulting)
can I have a chance to be involved?

480
00:24:27,699 --> 00:24:28,899
You're quite well-informed.

481
00:24:29,778 --> 00:24:31,098
I want to learn more from you.

482
00:24:34,018 --> 00:24:34,518
Mr. Li,

483
00:24:34,818 --> 00:24:35,459
you need me?

484
00:24:36,258 --> 00:24:37,018
You go ahead.

485
00:24:39,938 --> 00:24:41,474
(Chinese Imported Liquor Market
Preliminary Research)

486
00:24:43,338 --> 00:24:43,859
Mr. Li,

487
00:24:44,859 --> 00:24:48,058
is Qiao Hailun also going to
work on the GST project?

488
00:24:48,338 --> 00:24:50,818
It's only natural she knows
about such a big project.

489
00:24:52,778 --> 00:24:53,578
What do you think?

490
00:24:54,139 --> 00:24:56,098
I... I don't really have any thoughts.

491
00:24:56,659 --> 00:24:59,179
I'm having dinner
with GST's senior management tonight.

492
00:24:59,619 --> 00:25:00,328
Come along.

493
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,538
No problem. That's great.

494
00:25:04,139 --> 00:25:05,219
Thank you, Mr. Li.

495
00:25:13,538 --> 00:25:14,538
Sexual harassment?

496
00:25:16,338 --> 00:25:17,258
Sexual harassment?

497
00:25:18,738 --> 00:25:20,018
Fed up with a peaceful life?

498
00:25:20,859 --> 00:25:21,619
What did I do?

499
00:25:22,058 --> 00:25:24,058
What did you do?
Don't you know what you did?

500
00:25:25,498 --> 00:25:26,899
Must liquor sellers be young girls?

501
00:25:27,578 --> 00:25:29,219
It's all due to that wretch, Zhao Mei.

502
00:25:29,899 --> 00:25:31,338
I told you to stay away from her.

503
00:25:31,498 --> 00:25:32,488
But you wouldn't listen.

504
00:25:32,699 --> 00:25:34,058
What nonsense are you talking?

505
00:25:35,939 --> 00:25:36,459
Who is it?

506
00:25:37,018 --> 00:25:39,338
It's me.

507
00:25:43,258 --> 00:25:46,058
I came to bring something for Mr. Xu.

508
00:26:04,738 --> 00:26:06,058
Here are your office items.

509
00:26:06,939 --> 00:26:08,578
See if anything's missing.

510
00:26:12,578 --> 00:26:13,738
You stabbed me in the back.

511
00:26:14,859 --> 00:26:16,018
Now you play the good guy?

512
00:26:18,738 --> 00:26:19,338
What?

513
00:26:19,859 --> 00:26:20,459
What?

514
00:26:23,258 --> 00:26:24,899
First, you warned me to be careful.

515
00:26:25,818 --> 00:26:27,538
Then, I got set up in a honey trap.

516
00:26:28,098 --> 00:26:29,219
If not you, then who?

517
00:26:31,179 --> 00:26:31,679
Yes.

518
00:26:32,379 --> 00:26:33,179
It was me.

519
00:26:34,338 --> 00:26:35,419
After all, once you're out,

520
00:26:35,738 --> 00:26:37,298
I stand to gain the most.

521
00:26:37,419 --> 00:26:38,338
Cut your nonsense.

522
00:26:39,459 --> 00:26:41,098
That woman who set me up worked for you.

523
00:26:41,098 --> 00:26:42,018
My person harmed you?

524
00:26:42,018 --> 00:26:43,298
You harmed my person.

525
00:26:43,818 --> 00:26:45,738
You harassed her
and forced a kiss on her.

526
00:26:45,939 --> 00:26:47,058
Don't twist the truth.

527
00:26:47,778 --> 00:26:49,578
It's your person
who got us into this mess.

528
00:26:49,659 --> 00:26:50,939
How dare you say that?

529
00:26:50,939 --> 00:26:51,659
You shut up.

530
00:26:52,104 --> 00:26:53,352
Stay out of it. Go upstairs.

531
00:26:53,538 --> 00:26:54,038
You...

532
00:27:01,219 --> 00:27:03,498
So now everything is my fault, is it?

533
00:27:03,498 --> 00:27:05,258
You're all pinning the blame on me.

534
00:27:05,578 --> 00:27:07,979
If your employee
hadn't broken the rules by toasting me,

535
00:27:08,298 --> 00:27:09,699
none of this would have happened.

536
00:27:10,459 --> 00:27:11,818
She toasted you.

537
00:27:12,098 --> 00:27:13,659
You kissed her because she toasted you?

538
00:27:13,659 --> 00:27:14,619
What logic is that?

539
00:27:14,859 --> 00:27:16,018
It's perfectly normal logic.

540
00:27:16,498 --> 00:27:18,498
So many people hook up
in nightclubs each night.

541
00:27:18,699 --> 00:27:20,179
Why is it harassment when it's me?

542
00:27:20,578 --> 00:27:21,778
She left her spot

543
00:27:21,859 --> 00:27:23,459
and walked all the way over to toast me.

544
00:27:23,818 --> 00:27:25,058
That's quite a distance.

545
00:27:25,338 --> 00:27:27,538
If she wasn't willing, who forced her?

546
00:27:28,219 --> 00:27:29,179
As a sales lady,

547
00:27:29,699 --> 00:27:31,098
she knows she can't drink at work.

548
00:27:31,498 --> 00:27:32,619
Yet she came to toast.

549
00:27:33,098 --> 00:27:33,818
What did she want?

550
00:27:34,098 --> 00:27:35,778
You were the one holding her.

551
00:27:35,979 --> 00:27:37,699
That was your doing.

552
00:27:37,859 --> 00:27:39,258
And someone caught it on camera.

553
00:27:39,619 --> 00:27:40,578
Do you hug and kiss

554
00:27:40,578 --> 00:27:42,179
everyone who toasts you?

555
00:27:42,179 --> 00:27:43,379
If it were me toasting you?

556
00:27:43,379 --> 00:27:44,219
What would you do?

557
00:27:52,619 --> 00:27:53,738
Come down and get the door.

558
00:27:54,058 --> 00:27:54,979
Don't you have hands?

559
00:28:01,619 --> 00:28:02,419
Who is it?

560
00:28:03,139 --> 00:28:05,179
Hello. I'm Qi Youlan.
I need to see Mr. Xu.

561
00:28:12,298 --> 00:28:13,058
You planned this?

562
00:28:13,578 --> 00:28:14,258
No.

563
00:28:15,219 --> 00:28:16,379
She can't see me here.

564
00:28:24,139 --> 00:28:24,639
Wait.

565
00:28:32,498 --> 00:28:33,098
Mr. Xu.

566
00:28:34,379 --> 00:28:35,018
Please come in.

567
00:28:35,578 --> 00:28:36,078
Okay.

568
00:28:42,498 --> 00:28:43,219
What do you want?

569
00:28:45,699 --> 00:28:47,699
Seems you're quite popular, Mr. Xu.

570
00:28:51,379 --> 00:28:53,619
State your business.
I don't have time for chit-chat.

571
00:28:54,978 --> 00:28:56,139
(Qi Youlan,
Deputy HR Director, GST Liquor China)

572
00:28:56,139 --> 00:28:58,979
Are we going to talk standing?

573
00:28:59,459 --> 00:29:01,979
You're welcome to lie on the floor
if you don't mind the cold.

574
00:29:10,098 --> 00:29:11,939
Yes, I was drunk.

575
00:29:13,459 --> 00:29:14,538
Haven't you people?

576
00:29:14,979 --> 00:29:16,258
Everyone at GST,

577
00:29:16,778 --> 00:29:18,258
Barry, Peter,

578
00:29:18,379 --> 00:29:19,578
those old goats in management,

579
00:29:19,578 --> 00:29:20,738
and you, Qi Youlan.

580
00:29:21,258 --> 00:29:23,058
You all know very well how you act

581
00:29:23,298 --> 00:29:24,338
when you're drunk.

582
00:29:24,699 --> 00:29:27,419
Our drunken behavior
wasn't plastered online.

583
00:29:28,179 --> 00:29:30,058
The issue now is the public sentiment.

584
00:29:30,659 --> 00:29:32,538
Public opinion
is very much against you, Mr. Xu.

585
00:29:32,538 --> 00:29:34,979
This isn't 'public opinion'.
It's cyberbullying.

586
00:29:35,659 --> 00:29:36,939
I'm being bullied online.

587
00:29:37,459 --> 00:29:38,738
I was set up.

588
00:29:39,219 --> 00:29:40,578
And you guys aren't protecting me.

589
00:29:40,778 --> 00:29:42,219
You... You're accomplices.

590
00:29:44,619 --> 00:29:45,119
No.

591
00:29:47,258 --> 00:29:49,899
You're not accomplices.
You're the masterminds.

592
00:29:50,498 --> 00:29:51,979
You've lost your mind.

593
00:29:52,419 --> 00:29:54,979
You wanted me gone
but couldn't find a way,

594
00:29:55,498 --> 00:29:57,179
so you set up this scheme to frame me.

595
00:29:58,058 --> 00:30:00,578
Do you know your biggest problem?

596
00:30:01,219 --> 00:30:02,058
Arrogance.

597
00:30:03,058 --> 00:30:06,419
GST is a company with annual sales
reaching twenty billion dollars,

598
00:30:06,419 --> 00:30:11,578
controlling half the resources of
the world's most famous liquor brands.

599
00:30:11,778 --> 00:30:13,859
How could we possibly
risk the company's reputation

600
00:30:14,338 --> 00:30:16,338
for the sake of merely you?

601
00:30:16,498 --> 00:30:17,659
The reality is,

602
00:30:17,979 --> 00:30:19,058
precisely because of you,

603
00:30:19,219 --> 00:30:22,899
the company is facing
unprecedented public backlash.

604
00:30:23,338 --> 00:30:24,818
We're suffering significant losses.

605
00:30:25,098 --> 00:30:25,778
So what?

606
00:30:26,699 --> 00:30:28,939
The company should stand
by its employees,

607
00:30:29,219 --> 00:30:30,179
but you're not.

608
00:30:30,699 --> 00:30:32,139
You're kicking me while I'm down.

609
00:30:32,738 --> 00:30:34,419
You want to fire me, right?

610
00:30:37,738 --> 00:30:39,058
I'll be staying with my parents.

611
00:30:39,592 --> 00:30:41,064
The kid will go there after school.

612
00:30:56,179 --> 00:30:57,179
The company also wants

613
00:30:58,018 --> 00:30:59,778
to resolve this matter
as soon as possible.

614
00:31:01,939 --> 00:31:04,619
Mr. Xu, you should resign immediately.

615
00:31:06,778 --> 00:31:08,419
So desperate to save on severance pay?

616
00:31:12,538 --> 00:31:15,018
You could interpret it that way.

617
00:31:15,018 --> 00:31:16,179
Every cent counts.

618
00:31:16,459 --> 00:31:19,498
Of course, you have another option,
which is termination.

619
00:31:20,298 --> 00:31:22,298
That would mean

620
00:31:24,179 --> 00:31:24,859
changing careers

621
00:31:25,338 --> 00:31:27,179
or starting over completely.

622
00:31:27,498 --> 00:31:29,459
This isn't a threat, Mr. Xu.

623
00:31:29,699 --> 00:31:31,338
I'm just stating facts.

624
00:31:31,338 --> 00:31:32,258
No need.

625
00:31:32,699 --> 00:31:34,859
Tell them it's impossible.

626
00:31:35,338 --> 00:31:36,818
I understand how you feel.

627
00:31:37,098 --> 00:31:38,298
I'll give you a few days.

628
00:31:38,578 --> 00:31:40,872
But not too long. Get back to me soon.

629
00:31:41,178 --> 00:31:43,778
The company hopes to resolve this matter
as soon as possible.

630
00:31:43,778 --> 00:31:44,778
I'm sure you want

631
00:31:44,778 --> 00:31:47,699
to bring your wife
and kid home quickly, right?

632
00:31:49,298 --> 00:31:50,459
Who do you think you are?

633
00:31:51,538 --> 00:31:53,338
Don't think you can talk to me like this

634
00:31:53,338 --> 00:31:54,699
because Barry has your back.

635
00:31:56,179 --> 00:31:58,298
When I was building my career at GST,

636
00:31:59,098 --> 00:32:00,859
you were probably still playing in mud.

637
00:32:02,098 --> 00:32:04,179
Nothing you say will anger me.

638
00:32:05,459 --> 00:32:08,139
Because you've completely
lost your mind.

639
00:32:08,379 --> 00:32:09,379
But one thing's clear.

640
00:32:09,899 --> 00:32:13,379
From your statements and excuses,

641
00:32:14,578 --> 00:32:15,578
it's perfectly clear

642
00:32:16,699 --> 00:32:17,659
that you're shameless.

643
00:32:18,179 --> 00:32:18,899
What did you say?

644
00:32:19,619 --> 00:32:21,018
Workplace boundaries training.

645
00:32:21,619 --> 00:32:22,538
You've attended it.

646
00:32:22,538 --> 00:32:23,258
Don't deny it.

647
00:32:23,699 --> 00:32:26,538
I personally trained
all directors in China.

648
00:32:26,859 --> 00:32:27,859
Now you're telling me

649
00:32:27,859 --> 00:32:29,899
some girl threw herself at you
while you were drunk?

650
00:32:30,058 --> 00:32:32,578
Do you realize how ridiculous
and shameless that sounds?

651
00:32:32,578 --> 00:32:33,859
Don't push me. I'm warning you.

652
00:32:33,859 --> 00:32:34,659
I can push harder.

653
00:32:34,778 --> 00:32:36,018
You have a daughter.

654
00:32:36,018 --> 00:32:37,738
Show some decency, Mr. Xu.

655
00:32:38,338 --> 00:32:40,659
Say one more word and I'll kill you.

656
00:32:41,699 --> 00:32:42,419
Get back here.

657
00:32:56,139 --> 00:32:57,379
(Hello, Ms. Qi?)

658
00:32:57,659 --> 00:32:58,859
(Zhao Mei, where are you?)

659
00:32:59,338 --> 00:33:01,098
(Did you deliver the items
to Xu Yuntian?)

660
00:33:02,139 --> 00:33:03,659
(No, who said that?)

661
00:33:03,659 --> 00:33:05,219
(Come to my office now.)

662
00:33:06,899 --> 00:33:07,939
(Yes, Ms. Qi.)

663
00:33:08,258 --> 00:33:09,778
(The 24th floor
requires separate access.)

664
00:33:10,258 --> 00:33:11,899
Return this to me when you come down.

665
00:33:14,619 --> 00:33:15,119
Thanks.

666
00:33:31,899 --> 00:33:33,018
Hello, I'm...

667
00:33:35,018 --> 00:33:35,976
Names are on the doors.

668
00:33:40,538 --> 00:33:41,139
Thank you.

669
00:33:42,338 --> 00:33:43,419
(Such a show-off.)

670
00:34:05,058 --> 00:34:06,051
(Wang Jianxin)

671
00:34:09,419 --> 00:34:12,138
(So this is the 24th floor.)

672
00:34:12,979 --> 00:34:14,658
(It's like another world.)

673
00:34:25,498 --> 00:34:28,138
(Downstairs, we're practically
stacked on each other.)

674
00:34:28,939 --> 00:34:31,859
(Up here? They could roll around)

675
00:34:31,859 --> 00:34:32,578
(Qi Youlan)
(freely.)

676
00:34:37,339 --> 00:34:39,939
(So this is how the money gets spent.)

677
00:34:42,459 --> 00:34:43,939
I'll await your good news then.

678
00:34:45,259 --> 00:34:47,459
Don't worry, Ms. Qi.
I'll fight this for both of us.

679
00:34:48,839 --> 00:34:49,339
Ms. Qi.

680
00:34:49,339 --> 00:34:49,939
Come in.

681
00:34:53,064 --> 00:34:53,859
What a coincidence.

682
00:34:56,859 --> 00:34:58,018
She called you here too?

683
00:34:58,138 --> 00:34:59,018
You go ahead.

684
00:35:01,538 --> 00:35:02,178
(Bad feeling.)

685
00:35:02,698 --> 00:35:03,859
(That guy is plotting.)

686
00:35:08,739 --> 00:35:09,339
Ms. Qi.

687
00:35:09,658 --> 00:35:11,618
You want me at the briefing?

688
00:35:12,739 --> 00:35:13,259
Yes.

689
00:35:13,459 --> 00:35:15,899
Public opinion
is strongly against us now.

690
00:35:16,379 --> 00:35:17,618
Even the HQ knows.

691
00:35:18,739 --> 00:35:20,538
Management wants a briefing

692
00:35:20,739 --> 00:35:22,979
to have you explain everything.

693
00:35:27,498 --> 00:35:28,779
Am I the only one going?

694
00:35:29,538 --> 00:35:31,138
What about the rest of the sales team?

695
00:35:31,779 --> 00:35:34,259
You were there yesterday. That's enough.

696
00:35:37,018 --> 00:35:40,098
Ms. Qi, this seems inappropriate.

697
00:35:40,658 --> 00:35:42,739
Many people witnessed that night.

698
00:35:43,498 --> 00:35:46,618
If only I report to management,

699
00:35:47,138 --> 00:35:50,299
it'll look like
this was entirely my fault.

700
00:35:51,259 --> 00:35:52,739
Aren't you responsible?

701
00:35:55,979 --> 00:35:57,779
If your sales lady hadn't

702
00:35:57,779 --> 00:35:59,339
toasted Xu Yuntian,

703
00:35:59,979 --> 00:36:01,618
this wouldn't have happened.

704
00:36:01,899 --> 00:36:03,819
My sales lady violated rules first,

705
00:36:04,698 --> 00:36:06,779
so I fired her on the spot.

706
00:36:09,618 --> 00:36:11,178
That's my second point.

707
00:36:11,819 --> 00:36:13,178
Why fire her immediately?

708
00:36:13,979 --> 00:36:15,459
Couldn't you have waited?

709
00:36:16,218 --> 00:36:17,739
Because of your rash firing,

710
00:36:17,739 --> 00:36:20,658
people online are all saying
GST is an extremely cruel company.

711
00:36:21,138 --> 00:36:23,739
Xu Yuntian sexually harassed
the sales ladies.

712
00:36:23,979 --> 00:36:26,578
Xu Yuntian got off scot-free,
but the victim got fired.

713
00:36:27,538 --> 00:36:29,259
Wasn't it your decision-making error?

714
00:36:29,739 --> 00:36:32,739
When sales ladies make mistakes,
it's usually handled on the spot.

715
00:36:32,739 --> 00:36:35,379
This is also to warn other sales ladies
not to make mistakes.

716
00:36:36,018 --> 00:36:36,979
It's standard practice.

717
00:36:36,979 --> 00:36:38,939
Don't use it as an excuse
for your incompetence.

718
00:36:39,859 --> 00:36:41,259
When you were handling this matter,

719
00:36:41,259 --> 00:36:44,098
didn't you consider
if it might be recorded and posted?

720
00:36:44,098 --> 00:36:45,739
Didn't you think about what consequences

721
00:36:45,739 --> 00:36:47,259
it might bring for the company

722
00:36:47,259 --> 00:36:49,058
by firing the sales ladies on the spot?

723
00:36:49,899 --> 00:36:50,618
The key point is,

724
00:36:51,138 --> 00:36:53,819
you still don't realize
your own problem right now.

725
00:36:55,658 --> 00:36:58,259
This is not the kind of management

726
00:36:58,259 --> 00:37:01,379
a company needs during its development.

727
00:37:10,018 --> 00:37:12,018
Alright, go back and prepare.

728
00:37:12,899 --> 00:37:16,379
Explain the whole incident clearly
to management at tomorrow's meeting.

729
00:37:16,899 --> 00:37:17,399
Also,

730
00:37:18,218 --> 00:37:20,379
coordinate with PR team
for damage control.

731
00:37:20,739 --> 00:37:22,098
They will contact you anytime.

732
00:37:34,259 --> 00:37:35,578
(I guessed exactly right.)

733
00:37:35,899 --> 00:37:37,498
(They're making me the scapegoat again.)

734
00:37:37,899 --> 00:37:39,299
(The bullying just never stops.)

735
00:38:00,042 --> 00:38:04,782
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

736
00:38:09,232 --> 00:38:11,152
♪Too much of shame♪

737
00:38:11,498 --> 00:38:14,294
♪To waste it crying♪

738
00:38:16,752 --> 00:38:18,672
♪Leave all behind you♪

739
00:38:18,672 --> 00:38:20,952
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

740
00:38:21,072 --> 00:38:23,301
♪You know how far you've gone♪

741
00:38:23,436 --> 00:38:25,712
♪In the fire you rise again♪

742
00:38:25,898 --> 00:38:28,258
♪You made it through the worst♪

743
00:38:28,396 --> 00:38:30,600
♪The best is yet to come♪

744
00:38:30,843 --> 00:38:32,983
♪The best is yet to come♪

745
00:38:35,685 --> 00:38:37,008
♪Isn't it magical♪

746
00:38:37,008 --> 00:38:38,640
♪Listen, look,
how beautiful the night is♪

747
00:38:38,672 --> 00:38:41,139
♪With countless lights on,
is someone heartbroken again♪

748
00:38:41,139 --> 00:38:43,592
♪The sound of a heart
shattering on the ground is so crisp♪

749
00:38:43,673 --> 00:38:46,321
♪Turn on a light.
A lonely heart needs comfort♪

750
00:38:46,410 --> 00:38:48,941
♪Sweat, toil, dawn, dusk♪

751
00:38:49,021 --> 00:38:51,243
♪Devaluing self-respect
just for some hot food♪

752
00:38:51,385 --> 00:38:52,466
♪But I don't want to♪

753
00:38:52,575 --> 00:38:54,841
♪Sell dignity at a price,
trampling on past vows♪

754
00:38:54,957 --> 00:38:56,022
♪Until 3 AM♪

755
00:38:56,193 --> 00:38:57,398
♪Locking dreams away in a drawer♪

756
00:38:57,552 --> 00:38:58,785
♪Just to earn some meager profit♪

757
00:38:58,876 --> 00:39:01,240
♪No matter how hard I try,
it only brings sobs♪

758
00:39:01,387 --> 00:39:05,797
♪Renewing yearly, gone with no return,
teetering, utterly bland♪

759
00:39:20,522 --> 00:39:21,958
♪Leave all behind you♪

760
00:39:22,062 --> 00:39:24,549
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

761
00:39:24,732 --> 00:39:26,861
♪You know how far you've gone♪

762
00:39:27,048 --> 00:39:29,388
♪In the fire you rise again♪

763
00:39:29,456 --> 00:39:31,722
♪You made it through the worst♪

764
00:39:32,082 --> 00:39:34,160
♪The best is yet to come♪

765
00:39:34,409 --> 00:39:36,579
♪The best is yet to come♪

766
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,432
♪Isn't it magical♪

767
00:39:40,432 --> 00:39:44,078
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

768
00:39:44,112 --> 00:39:45,968
♪And I see them sparkling♪

769
00:39:46,192 --> 00:39:48,323
♪Nobody knows♪

770
00:39:48,944 --> 00:39:50,854
♪What tomorrow brings♪

771
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:53,443
♪You made it through the worst♪

772
00:39:53,630 --> 00:39:55,838
♪The best is yet to come♪

773
00:39:56,125 --> 00:39:58,274
♪The best is yet to come♪

774
00:39:58,570 --> 00:39:59,984
♪Isn't it magical♪

775
00:39:59,984 --> 00:40:02,196
♪Feeling uneasy,
yet no one's chasing me♪

776
00:40:02,270 --> 00:40:04,624
♪Retreating step by step,
everything turning to ash♪

777
00:40:04,624 --> 00:40:05,712
♪I'm silent, I'm roaring♪

778
00:40:05,712 --> 00:40:09,163
♪This helplessness
keeps pushing me towards the cliff♪

779
00:40:09,616 --> 00:40:11,890
♪Trembling legs
carry away a shattered soul♪

780
00:40:12,304 --> 00:40:13,168
♪Who wants to be just a passerby♪

781
00:40:13,168 --> 00:40:14,688
♪Isn't it magical♪
